<div class="comment" id="comment9355">
  <p class="banner"><a href="/web/20100506231215/http://ja.doukaku.org/user/1025/" target="_top">tanakahisateru</a><a href="/web/20100506231215/http://ja.doukaku.org/qa/#anomark" target="_top"><img src="/web/20100506231215im_/http://ja.doukaku.org/static/image/anomark.png" border=0/></a>

	
	&nbsp;
	<a href="/web/20100506231215/http://ja.doukaku.org/comment/9355/">#9355</a>(<script language="JavaScript">print_time(new Date("2009/07/13 15:05 GMT"));</script><noscript>2009/07/13 15:05 GMT</noscript>)
	
	
	
	[<a href="/web/20100506231215/http://ja.doukaku.org/lang/python/">
	  Python
	</a>]
	
	
	
	&nbsp;

<span class="rating">評価<span style="background-color: #ffffff;">0/0=0.00</span></span>
  </p>
  <div class="comment_content">
	<div class="comment_body">
	  <p>すみません、ログインせずに書いたうえ、バグありでした。__setattr__の正しい実装はこうです。</p>

	</div>
	
	
	
    <div class="compact">
      <table><tr><td class="linenos"><pre>1
2
3
4</pre></td><td class="code"><div class="highlight"><pre>    <span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">__setattr__</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">attr</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">value</span><span class="p">):</span>
        <span class="k">if</span> <span class="ow">not</span> <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">cfg</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">has_section</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#39;default&#39;</span><span class="p">):</span>
            <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">cfg</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">add_section</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#39;default&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>
        <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">cfg</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">set</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#39;default&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">attr</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">value</span><span class="p">)</span>
</pre></div>
</td></tr></table>
    </div>
	

  
